caption.body: NOW PLAYING: An introverted young man finds comfort, confidence, and freedom while dressing in women’s clothing until coming upon his father in a chance encounter on a busy street in this beautifully composed and restrained film by Yuchao Feng.  See "Red" by Yuchao Feng, now playing in the Video Arts Room located pre-security in the International Terminal. http://bit.ly/2K6RM8N
